result.execSummary:
The defendant Davina L Johnson was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Davina L Johnson is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Davina L Johnson was found guilty of 2nd Degree Reckless Homicide, a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.06(1).
